  "description": "<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Idi na trideset brojeva.</p>\n<p>U kineskom, broj 30 se zove <ruby>三十<rp>(</rp><rt>sān shí</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>.</p>\n<p>Brojevi od 31 do 39 formiraju se dodavanjem kineskog broja jedinice (1–9) nakon <ruby>三十<rp>(</rp><rt>sān shí</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby> (30).</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\">Broj</th>\n<th align=\"left\">Kinijski</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">30</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><ruby>三十<rp>(</rp><rt>sān shí</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">31</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><ruby>三十一<rp>(</rp><rt>sān shí yī</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">32</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><ruby>三十二<rp>(</rp><rt>sān shí èr</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">33</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><ruby>三十三<rp>(</rp><rt>sān shí sān</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">34</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><ruby>三十四<rp>(</rp><rt>sān shí sì</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">35</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><ruby>三十五<rp>(</rp><rt>sān shí wǔ</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">36</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><ruby>三十六<rp>(</rp><rt>sān shí liù</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">37</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><ruby>三十七<rp>(</rp><rt>sān shí qī</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">38</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><ruby>三十八<rp>(</rp><rt>sān shí bā</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">39</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><ruby>三十九<rp>(</rp><rt>sān shí jiǔ</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</section>",
